e="preserve">Jannine Weigel (Thai: ญานนีน ภารวี ไวเกล; born 30 July 2000) Is a Thai singer and actor With Thai and German ancestry She is famous for cover the music on YouTube. With a YouTube channel called Jannine Weigel. Made her famous for music by covering her music on YouTube Until becoming an artist under GMM Grammy She is currently an independent artist. Live happily in Germany
Early life.
Jannine Weigel was born in Steinfurt. In Germany and grew there until the age of 10 in July 2010. Her family moved to Thailand. She has 3 brothers and sisters. She is the youngest child. Graduated from kindergarten from St Martin. Steinfurt city Germany Graduated from elementary school At the school Regen Boken Chulay Steinfurt city Germany Study a bachelor's degree in advance, achievement card, Sukhothai Thammathirat Open University Faculty of Liberal Arts Department of English And graduated from junior high school with a distance education institution
